import java.nio.file.{ Files, Paths }
import scala.collection.mutable.ListBuffer
import java.io.FileWriter
val fw = new FileWriter("/home/ama/sidana/kelkoo_may_june_stats/offerViewStats_4.txt", true)
//val countryCodes = Array("at","be","br","ch","cz","de","dk","es","fi","ie","nb","nl","no","pl","pt","ru","se","uk")
val countryCodes = Array("it")
//,"no","pl","pt","ru","se","uk"
for (code <- countryCodes){
val parquetFileClick = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypso_data_may_june/calypso_data_may_june/offerView/"+code+"/2016/*/*/*.parquet")
val uniqueUsers = parquetFileClick.select("userId").distinct.count
val uniqueOffers = parquetFileClick.select("offerViewId").distinct.count
val observedNumberOfRatings = parquetFileClick.select("userId","offerViewId").distinct.count
val uniqueOfferCategories = parquetFileClick.select("category").distinct.count
val numOffersShown = parquetFileClick.count
fw.write(code+","+ numOffersShown +","+uniqueUsers+","+uniqueOffers+","+observedNumberOfRatings+","+uniqueOfferCategories+"\n")
}
fw.close()
